How to Participate?
🎁 Like this post
🎁 Follow @giveaways.sg & @kundalsg.official & @thetattletaleagency
🎁 Tell us what is your favourite KUNDAL fragrance
🎁 Tag a friend and leave a comment with your answer to the above question!

Winners will receive their gifts by mail.
T&Cs apply. We reserve the right to modify the T&Cs without any prior notice. Only applicable for Singapore residents. This giveaway is in no way sponsored, endorsed or administered by Instagram. Winners will be announced on this post.
